name: Travel Toil
description: Welcome to Travel Toil. You, (an unseen character) have been working ever so hard during the year and are looking for a way to celebrate so what better way than a vacation? However, there's just one problem, you haven't exactly been keeping up with your funds and have no idea how much money you have. Will you be lucky and get to travel anyway or will you be forced to have a staycation?
